        "cooked": "<p>Updated 27th November 2004</p>\n<p><span class=\"bbcode-b\"><a href=\"http://chaosfish.free.fr/mbn/LBAfileinfo.zip\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Download LBA File Information</a></span> - HTML Help document[b]</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chaosfish.free.fr/lbafileinfo/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">View LBA File Information online</a>[/b]</p>\n<p>LBA File Information: The project is a document that contains LBA file information. The document currently only includes packages content, and that too is still mostly incomplete.<br>\nThe goal of the project is to have all information possible about the LBA files.</p>\n<p>Currently having:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>LBA1\n<ul>\n<li>HQR\n<ul>\n<li>ANIM.HQR</li>\n<li>BODY.HQR</li>\n<li>FILE3D.HQR</li>\n<li>FLA_GIF.HQR</li>\n<li>INVOBJ.HQR</li>\n<li>LBA_GRI.HQR (incomplete)</li>\n<li>RESS.HQR</li>\n<li>SAMPLES.HQR (needs rewrite)</li>\n<li>SCENE.HQR</li>\n<li>SPRITES.HQR (needs a bit work)</li>\n<li>TEXT.HQR</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>VOX\n<ul>\n<li>English\n<ul>\n<li>EN_GAM.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_000.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_001.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_002.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_003.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_004.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_005.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_006.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_007.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_008.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_009.VOX</li>\n<li>EN_010.VOX</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>French\n<ul>\n<li>FR_GAM.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_000.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_001.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_002.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_003.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_004.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_005.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_006.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_007.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_008.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_009.VOX</li>\n<li>FR_010.VOX</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>German</li>\n<li>DE_GAM.VOX\n<ul>\n<li>DE_000.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_001.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_002.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_003.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_004.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_005.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_006.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_007.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_008.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_009.VOX</li>\n<li>DE_010.VOX</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>LBA2\n<ul>\n<li>HQR\n<ul>\n<li>BODY.HQR</li>\n<li>HOLOMAP.HQR</li>\n<li>LBA_BKG.HQR (incomplete)</li>\n<li>OBJFIX.HQR</li>\n<li>RESS.HQR (incomplete)</li>\n<li>SAMPLES.HQR(needs rewrite)</li>\n<li>SCENE.HQR</li>\n<li>SCREEN.HQR</li>\n<li>SCRSHOT.HQR</li>\n<li>SPRIRAW.HQR(incomplete)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>OBL\n<ul>\n<li>CITABAU.OBL</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want to contribute to the project check <a href=\"/t/submissions-for-lba-file-information/6707/1\">this thread</a>.</p>",
